8287 arm_status arm_dct4_init_q31(
8288  arm_dct4_instance_q31 * S,
8289  arm_rfft_instance_q31 * S_RFFT,
8290  arm_cfft_radix4_instance_q31 * S_CFFT,
8291  uint16_t N,
8292  uint16_t Nby2,
8293  q31_t normalize)
8294 {
8295  /* Initialise the default arm status */
8296  arm_status status = ARM_MATH_SUCCESS;
8297 
8298  /* Initializing the pointer array with the weight table base addresses of different lengths */
8299  q31_t *twiddlePtr[4] = { (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_128, (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_512,
8300  (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_2048, (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_8192
8301  };
8302 
8303  /* Initializing the pointer array with the cos factor table base addresses of different lengths */
8304  q31_t *pCosFactor[4] =
8305  { (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_128, (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_512,
8306  (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_2048, (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_8192
8307  };
8308 
8309  /* Initialize the DCT4 length */
8310  S->N = N;
8311 
8312  /* Initialize the half of DCT4 length */
8313  S->Nby2 = Nby2;
8314 
8315  /* Initialize the DCT4 Normalizing factor */
8316  S->normalize = normalize;
8317 
8318  /* Initialize Real FFT Instance */
8319  S->pRfft = S_RFFT;
8320 
8321  /* Initialize Complex FFT Instance */
8322  S->pCfft = S_CFFT;
8323 
8324  switch (N)
8325  {
8326  /* Initialize the table modifier values */
8327  case 8192u:
8328  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[3];
8329  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[3];
8330  break;
8331  case 2048u:
8332  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[2];
8333  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[2];
8334  break;
8335  case 512u:
8336  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[1];
8337  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[1];
8338  break;
8339  case 128u:
8340  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[0];
8341  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[0];
8342  break;
8343  default:
8344  status = ARM_MATH_ARGUMENT_ERROR;
8345  }
8346 
8347  /* Initialize the RFFT/RIFFT Function */
8348  arm_rfft_init_q31(S->pRfft, S->pCfft, S->N, 0, 1);
8349 
8350  /* return the status of DCT4 Init function */
8351  return (status);
8352 }
